_sText:
This is my first CS:S map, which is a remake of my favorite Tactical Ops map, TO-Cellar (sorry, I can't find the original author, nor the original map!).  The map was made from memory, so the details may be a little off but the map does play similarly (very fast, deathmatch-style play - hard to camp, although it is do-able)

I've also expanded the max number of players to 20 per team, so there should be plenty of room.
